Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.74,0:23:23.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(100,100)}有着寻求的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.37,0:23:25.94,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(100,100)}相信着
